<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20688873">关于王家卫有哪些有趣的故事？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="456029" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">有趣的故事比如：
<a href="http://www.wenzhangbaike.com/thread-439-1-1.html" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">王家卫和他的演员们的故事！<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br><a href="http://www.wenzhangbaike.com/thread-440-1-1.html" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">王家卫是磨神英雄坛斗士，多次逼得演员开溜。<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br><a href="http://www.wenzhangbaike.com/thread-441-1-1.html" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">王家卫背后女人的故事<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br>等等都算王家卫的故事。</div>


